biography.text: Gorgon City’s Kye Gibbon and Matt Robson Scott have firmly established themselves as one of the most revered contemporary dance music duos.  They have amassed to date over 15 million singles and 2 billion global streams, rewarded for their now distinctly recognisable sound of timeless, often bass driven, house music.
